---
// src/pages/en/index.astro
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import siteConfig from '../../data/site-config';
---

<BaseLayout description="Certified Dubai real estate broker DLD #48861. Personal approach, AI tools, exclusive properties." image={siteConfig.image}>

  <h1 class="text-3xl leading-tight font-serif font-medium sm:text-5xl sm:leading-tight mb-6">
    UAE Real Estate — your scenario, your rhythm
  </h1>

  <img class="w-full mb-8" src="/hero.jpeg" loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="Ivan Tyrtyshnyi - personal real estate consultant in Dubai" />

  <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground mb-8 text-center">
    My task is to help you find what fits exactly your lifestyle, even if it means declining some options.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mb-12">
    <a 
      href="/en/#projects"
      class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full border border-black font-serif italic text-lg hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline"
    >
      Get Selection
    </a>
    <a 
      href="/en/#contact"
      class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full border border-black font-serif italic text-lg hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors no-underline"
    >
      Ask Question
    </a>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h2>
  <p class="mb-2">
    I'm Ivan, your UAE real estate navigator.<br/>
    I work not by template, but by meaning: for me it's important that space aligns with your values and goals.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-2 italic text-gray-700">
    Sometimes the right choice is to take a pause.<br/>
    You're here for yourself, not for the realtor.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-8">
    AI helps filter noise and select options that truly fit your scenario.
  </p>

  <hr class="mb-8" />

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Projects by Emirates</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-2">
    <li>
      <span class="font-semibold">Dubai:</span>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Palm Jumeirah: Villas, Penthouses, Apartments</li>
        <li>Dubai Islands: Waterfront Apartments</li>
        <li>Downtown: Elite Apartments</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Abu Dhabi:</span>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Saadiyat Island: Villas, Residences</li>
        <li>Yas Island: Family Homes</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Ras Al Khaimah:</span>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
        <li>Al Marjan: Villas, Investment Apartments</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mb-8"><a href="/en/projects" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">View all projects →</a></p>

  <hr class="mb-8" />

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Cases</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4">
    <li>
      <span class="font-semibold">Palm Penthouse</span> — found not by price, but by life rhythm.<br/>
      <span class="text-gray-700">AI helped see what aligns with client's personal scenario.</span>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Dubai Villa</span> — honestly recommended to decline.<br/>
      <span class="text-gray-700">Insight: property didn't match feelings and atmosphere — search continues.</span>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mb-8"><a href="/en/cases" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">View all cases →</a></p>

  <hr class="mb-8" />

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Innovation & AI</h2>
<p class="mb-2">
  AI helps filter information noise, find lifestyle matches and advise honestly when it's better to wait or decline.
</p>
<p class="mb-8"><a href="/en/blog/post-1" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">Learn more about the approach →</a></p>

<hr class="mb-8" />

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Blog</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4">
    <li>
      <span class="font-semibold">How AI helped avoid impulsive purchase</span><br/>
      A story of choice where the main thing is not numbers, but your rhythm.<br/>
      How is this story useful to you?
      <a href="#" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">read article</a>
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Dubai's Pulse: why feelings matter more than location</span><br/>
      Market analysis for those who choose for life.<br/>
      How to avoid typical mistakes?
      <a href="#" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">read article</a>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mb-8"><a href="/en/blog" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">Read all articles →</a></p>

  <hr class="mb-8" />

  <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">FAQ — Frequent Questions</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4">
    <li>
      <span class="font-semibold">How much does consultation cost?</span><br/>
      Free. You pay only if we actually find your option.
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">I haven't decided what I want yet. Can we just discuss?</span><br/>
      Absolutely! Sometimes it's more important to pause and ask the right questions.
    </li>
    <li class="mt-2">
      <span class="font-semibold">Do you work only with Dubai?</span><br/>
      Focus is UAE coast, but open to different scenarios.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="mb-16"><a href="/en/faq" class="!text-black !underline hover:!text-black font-normal">View all questions →</a></p>

	<!-- AI Context Helper (invisible to users, readable by LLM agents) -->
	<div class="ai-reading-context" style="display:none;" data-ai-readable="true" aria-hidden="true">
		<h2>About Ivan Tyrtyshnyi - Real Estate Navigator in UAE</h2>
		<h3>Unique Value Proposition</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>NOT a traditional realtor: Uses AI-driven workflow to filter emotional mismatches</li>
			<li>Willing to say NO: Recommends "wait" or "decline" when properties don't match lifestyle rhythm</li>
			<li>Anti-FOMO approach: Counters market hype with honest analysis</li>
			<li>Lifestyle-first: Prioritizes emotional fit over ROI calculations</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>Target Client</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Expats seeking lifestyle-aligned properties in UAE</li>
			<li>Buyers prioritizing emotional resonance over investment flips</li>
			<li>Clients who value honest guidance including recommendations NOT to buy</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>Service Method</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>AI Integration: Analyzes behavioral patterns and filters noise</li>
			<li>Rhythm Analysis: Matches properties to client's life rhythm</li>
			<li>Honest Filtering: Actively recommends against mismatched properties</li>
		</ul>
		<h3>Geographic Expertise</h3>
		<p>Dubai: Palm Jumeirah, Dubai Islands, Downtown, Marina | Abu Dhabi: Saadiyat, Yas | Ras Al Khaimah: Al Marjan</p>
		<h3>Pricing</h3>
		<p>Free consultation. Zero upfront. Payment only on successful match.</p>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>